  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "A sawmill catches fire in Waskadu",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Kalutara North Police said that a large number of pallet boards prepared for import to foreign countries were destroyed in a fire that broke out in a wood mill in Waskaduwa last night (27th).",
        "The fire broke out in the section with the wood-seasoning boiler of the sawmill running behind a house in Vaskaduwa Gallupara.",
        "With the occurrence of the incident, a team consisting of six firemen of the Kalutara Municipal Council arrived and controlled the fire in about 45 minutes, but it was seen that all the pallets stored there were destroyed.",
        "The Kalutara Municipal Fire Fighting Unit states that the cause of the fire cannot be specified, and the damage has not yet been estimated."
      ],
      "title_ents": [
        {
          "text": "Waskadu",
          "label": "ORG"
        }
      ],
